### Crear una tarea
POST http://localhost:8080/api/task
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskTitle": "Tarea de ejemplo",
  "taskDescription": "Descripción de la tarea",
  "idState": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "createdAt": "2025-05-16T10:00:00",
  "updatedAt": "2025-05-16T10:00:00"
}

### Actualizar una tarea
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/task/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskTitle": "Tarea actualizada",
  "taskDescription": "Descripción actualizada",
  "idState": 2,
  "userId": 1,
  "createdAt": "2025-05-16T10:00:00",
  "updatedAt": "2025-05-16T12:00:00"
}

### Obtener una tarea por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task/1

### Eliminar una tarea
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/task/1
